name: Purple
description:
- 2" heavyweight polypropylene base (1800lbs. breaking strength) with two 1" polypro bottom straps (900lb. breaking strength). Polypropylene is water resistant.
- 1000 denier Cordura nylon  topside to spiff and stiffen them up.
- Industrial grade Velcro ensures zero slippage.
- Designed to fit most platform pedals.
- One size fits all. Designed to quickly and easily adjust to any shoe and foot size.
- Sold in sets of two. No pedals included.
